2026-04-23T04:53:54.2656433Z 12    <!--
2026-04-23T04:53:54.2656826Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-23T04:53:54.2657187Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
